    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144230/extras/f580426b2467807cff0f27c429a91726.poster.avif?t=1771501166\" width=780 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144230/extras/f580426b2467807cff0f27c429a91726.webm?t=1771501166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在游戏中体验现代及未来的军用载具</h2><br>现代战舰是一款跨平台多人对战类游戏。游戏中的战斗方式与现实中的现代海战如出一辙。侦察机前出在远距离发现目标，巡洋舰发射大量导弹对敌人近防系统进行饱和打击，而潜艇则将悄悄接近敌人水面舰艇，战斗机还将从空中掩护友军舰队。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >现代战争</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144230/extras/9117dd2f8bf9fcf8440a80a7cbe23af5.poster.avif?t=1771501166\" width=780 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144230/extras/9117dd2f8bf9fcf8440a80a7cbe23af5.webm?t=1771501166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>参与现代背景的海战和空战，并在游戏中体验符合真实性能的作战载具。游戏里还可以体验无人机和精确制导武器。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >所有顶级载具</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144230/extras/c759a3b8026e2134926a338cd78f66b3.poster.avif?t=1771501166\" width=780 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144230/extras/c759a3b8026e2134926a338cd78f66b3.webm?t=1771501166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>超过 200 款现代及计划建造的战舰和飞机，包括航空母舰，潜艇，无人机，隐身战斗机及战略轰炸机。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >动态且实用的游戏操作</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144230/extras/8ea4f6f1f5b876a66353f1b77096faea.poster.avif?t=1771501166\" width=780 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144230/extras/8ea4f6f1f5b876a66353f1b77096faea.webm?t=1771501166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>游戏拥有容易上手的操作方式以及充满趣味的街机战斗模式，因此您可以在一场战斗中在不同的载具类型之间无缝切换，让您能时刻置身于战场上最有趣的部分！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自己动手</h2><br>通过游戏中广泛的自定义系统，自行改装您的战舰和战机。几乎所有主要部件都可以更换。用超音速导弹的威力击毁敌人吧！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不会令人失望的优秀游戏</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144230/extras/ced23d5e3f3978f1a8a4b7a02b71a672.poster.avif?t=1771501166\" width=780 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144230/extras/ced23d5e3f3978f1a8a4b7a02b71a672.webm?t=1771501166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>现代战舰会定期进行更新，为游戏添加新地图，作战载具几武器系统，游戏中还会举行锦标赛及各种活动，为玩家带来全新游戏体验，从不同角度体验现代海战和空战。",
